1. *Raste* drvo u vrtu. (A tree is growing in the garden.)
2. Ljudi *rastu* u znanju. (People are growing in knowledge.)
3. *Rastu* cene sirovina. (Raw material prices are rising.)
4. Temperatura *rastu* iz dana u dan. (The temperature is rising day by day.)
5. Njihove nade *rastu* sa svakim danu. (Their hopes are growing with each day.)